  "original_title": "\u2019\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Teach army to maintain law and order'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Human Rights Commission has informed the Defense Secretary to issue instructions to the authorities to maintain law and order and to take steps to avoid recurrence of such incidents even though people are protesting in the crisis situation in the country.",
        "The Sri Lanka Human Rights Commission has informed Defense Secretary Kamal Gunaratne that the Sri Lanka Human Rights Commission has conducted inquiries regarding the recent incident of an army officer kicking a person during the chaos at Yakkahabitiya petrol station in Kurunegala.",
        "The Defense Secretary told the Commission that he as the Defense Secretary condemns the incident and the Army has started a high-level investigation in this regard. The Defense Secretary told the commission that necessary measures will be taken to prevent such incidents from happening again.",
        "Considering the prevailing situation in the country, the Chairman of the Human Rights Commission has informed the Defense Secretary to issue instructions to the authorities to maintain law and order and to take steps to prevent such incidents from happening again."
      ],
